                </span>
              </a>
              <a href="">
                <i class="fa fa-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <span>
                  booktopia@gmail.com
                </span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 info-col">
          <div class="info_detail">
            <h4>
              About Us
            </h4>
            <p>
              Booktopia is a free website for reading and writing stories. Follow us on our social platforms:
            </p>
            <div class="info_social">
              <a href="">
